{"tid":1659472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我是一位90後的台灣人，我徹底的為香港人而感到驕傲、自豪。","createTime":"2019-10-17T03:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T12:32:41.000Z","uid":156450,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"89549cb23c9a631071b74b0da35ec7ec8c2a39ad","tid":1659472,"uid":156450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:25:38.000Z","msg":"這四個月內，我們經歷過難熬的晚上、痛心疾首的意志、不被家人諒解的無奈、濫權的暴力震壓。<br />\n<br />\n我是一位90後的台灣人，我徹底的為香港人而感到驕傲、自豪。<br />\n<br />\n現今公利主義之下的社會，仍然存在大部分有良知的學生。香港人，最難能可貴的是能夠放棄短暫的自身利益，走上街頭為人民、為後代爭取本來就屬於我們的權利。雖然可笑，但其實可悲。<br />\n<br />\n自2014年的雨傘革命，我一直留意着香港政事，衷心希望能為香港人、為民主二字出一分綿力。我們就是有這股勁 ，無他，為的只是我們日後的路。<br />\n<br />\n今天，你們再次走上街頭，並不只是為香港而抗爭，甚是為了「民主自由」四字而戰。你們都是戰士。<br />\n<br />\n倘若有天，全球的民主自由都失去，誰再也不能為良知而說話，再也不能為公義而說理，人民都要活在極權、恐懼之下。 後果我們已經有前車之鑒，大家有目共睹，我們誰都不願再讓一步。<br />\n<br />\n很榮幸「PEPE THE FROG」能成為香港人抗爭的「代表人物」。小編我機緣巧合成為「PEPE THE FROG」亞洲代理。是緣。<br />\n<br />\n慶幸世上仍有良知之人，資本主義的世界下，活在資本兩字之上，不容易。<br />\n衷心感謝，尊敬。 <br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\nPEPE THE FROG<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B3hZGH0lvn7/?igshid=kpfq6b7nx3of\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB3hZGH0lvn7%2F%3Figshid%3Dkpfq6b7nx3of&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=f2427e00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB3hZGH0lvn7%2F%3Figshid%3Dkpfq6b7nx3of&h=033c26dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B3hZGH0lvn7/?igshid=kpfq6b7nx3of</a>"},{"pid":"2f74d32fce5278e3a9e4609a88d568934edd34f1","tid":1659472,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ba62a0f0ebdf0ade4be925d9820c8e5340313752","tid":1659472,"uid":289259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:27:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"> IG &ldquo;bye bye starbucks&rdquo; challenge</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659200</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手推啦各位，和理非出嚟啦。"},{"pid":"63fad7fd3b836d029ed11fd785341af64c1c77a0","tid":1659472,"uid":156450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T03:55:56.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"44be85fdbc08d7389c40868f124ecb7cf5533a68","tid":1659472,"uid":97776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:03:13.000Z","msg":"今天香港<br />\n明日台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cad95ab4eb7d87025d0fa3b2d219513a3960d49","tid":1659472,"uid":199235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:09:02.000Z","msg":"推.."},{"pid":"b4ed72dce51b30843da11e67a6631187ffde0fa3","tid":1659472,"uid":180745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"賣廣告？<br />\n樓主係轉貼定咩<br />\n你都唔係台灣人"},{"pid":"bb4f12e91bae34f83ed03901bc71bd41394f4e6d","tid":1659472,"uid":156450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4ed72dce51b30843da11e67a6631187ffde0fa3","tid":1659472,"uid":180745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"賣廣告？<br />\n樓主係轉貼定咩<br />\n你都唔係台灣人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:02:31.000Z","msg":"轉貼"},{"pid":"d9e6ad7a59bb4d1719939118a331bbb13f23b813","tid":1659472,"uid":180745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb4f12e91bae34f83ed03901bc71bd41394f4e6d","tid":1659472,"uid":156450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4ed72dce51b30843da11e67a6631187ffde0fa3","tid":1659472,"uid":180745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"賣廣告？<br />\n樓主係轉貼定咩<br />\n你都唔係台灣人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:02:31.000Z","msg":"轉貼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:12:11.000Z","